{"tid":145028,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"愛子公主1年暴瘦18公斤 BMI只有13.8達「重症等級」","createTime":"2017-03-06T02:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T12:57:05.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"44d72481be60165b4fec1227b4d45e468b1211df","tid":145028,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:24:42.000Z","msg":"日本皇太子德仁夫婦的掌上明珠「愛子公主」2016年曾傳出疑似遭同學霸凌，3個星期沒有上學，之後便暴瘦成紙片人，體重預測不到40公斤，外界揣測可能罹患厭食症。據週刊報導，她一年暴瘦18公斤，目前身高164公分體重僅有37公斤，BMI遠遠低於標準值，只有13.8，狀況很不樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2374/d2374101.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2374%2Fd2374101.jpg&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvgEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=5afdd55b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2374/d2374101.jpg</a><br />\n▲愛子公主1年暴瘦18公斤，目前BMI僅13.8。<br />\n<br />\n據《女性SEVEN》周刊報導，愛子公主1年前BMI值約20.4，在正常範圍內，但暑假時已經明顯清瘦不少，臉頰凹陷蒼白、看起來無精打采的模樣曾引起外界高度討論；有精神科醫師指出，當BMI低於17時需接受治療，低於15已經是重症等級，如果不立即接受治療，可能會危及生命。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2354/d2354212.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2354%2Fd2354212.jpg&h=6f8e74fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲德仁全家福近日曝光，愛子公主暴瘦引起關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.takungpao.com/2015/0403/20150403081816692.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.takungpao.com%2F2015%2F0403%2F20150403081816692.jpg&h=2dd6b142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.piutao.com/uploads/201412/p51qknnvhf2255.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.piutao.com%2Fuploads%2F201412%2Fp51qknnvhf2255.jpg&h=38ff6f6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲佳子公主真是好正啊。<br />\n<br />\n精神科醫師田中伸明強調，愛子公主目前的BMI值會導致新陳代謝、體力下降、賀爾蒙失調等問題，此外如果體重長期過輕，除了可能影響生育能力之外，還有腦部萎縮的可能，甚至因為長期追求更瘦的身材，很有可能罹患恐慌症，並產生輕生念頭，建議務必就醫治療。"},{"pid":"5e7ad3d17a2cc0b783d84488584261ce35815fa4","tid":145028,"uid":1914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:25:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448cfb39d64823644bcd3c96cf4a3a6a2c5f4b5e","tid":145028,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:25:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2374/d2374101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2374%2Fd2374101.jpg&h=f4a22941&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲愛子公主1年暴瘦18公斤，目前BMI僅13.8。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1c0ad020b3c92f5d3b44863a85213df051cbe738","tid":145028,"uid":2111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:57:11.000Z","msg":"無啦啦佳子公主好正阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c012453f77acc9460e6557c10fae3f2bc895478","tid":145028,"uid":36321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:10:12.000Z","msg":"本身都冇野<br />\n好死唔死個堂妹係靚女<br />\n比到有精神病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c7cdfeefb11f40364eca004d3ca4ef640bc94c","tid":145028,"uid":5702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:12:28.000Z","msg":"我覺得係d人成日笑鳩佢肥先搞成咁"},{"pid":"ea26cfd87cb167ff8077963ae9d91a27087c3563","tid":145028,"uid":38934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:15:20.000Z","msg":"明明以前脹卜卜好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132a5183b7b8651642332f0607d889987e4e4110","tid":145028,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:17:03.000Z","msg":"佳子公主: 你越墮落 我越快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gi